# Input

```md
[hello](#world)

[*](#styling-footnote)

[  spaced  ](#link)

[link](https://example.com "title")

[link](https://example.com "  spaced title  ")

text with [inline](link) in the middle

[link with **bold**](url)

[foo](<https://example.com>)

[encoded](https://www.google.fr/()foo->bar)

[encoded](<https://www.google.fr/()foo-%3Ebar>)

```


# Formatted

```md
[hello](#world)

[\*](#styling-footnote)

[  spaced  ](#link)

[link](https://example.com "title")

[link](https://example.com "  spaced title  ")

text with [inline](link) in the middle

[link with **bold**](url)

[foo](<https://example.com>)

[encoded](<https://www.google.fr/()foo-%3Ebar>)

[encoded](<https://www.google.fr/()foo-%3Ebar>)

```
